snippet.title: busking in Vancouver | her habits vlog
snippet.description:
Hey all you cool cats and kittens! I went busking in Vancouver, along the seawall. I must say it was an absolutely beautiful day and I had a lot of fun. I captured all the ins and outs and awkward moments for your enjoyment. Love you all!❤️ #busking #singersongwriter #canadianmusician #vancouver
